sentences: Marie-Thérèse Paquin,  was born July 4, 1905 in Montreal, Quebec, and died in the same city on May 9, 1997.
She had a brilliant career as a member of a quartet for 20 years.
She was pianist for the Montreal Symphony Orchestra from 1936 to 1964.
Marie-Thérèse Paquin, C.M., Membre (1980) de l'Order of Canada
Marie-Thérèse Vintrin-Paquin (1905 – 1997), Chevalière (1987) de l'Ordre national du Québec
